  "texts": [
    "Sixth, nearly half of all messages sent by adults were from users under the age of 26.",
    "Seventh, ChatGPT usage has grown especially fast over the last year in low-and middle-income countries.",
    "Eighth, we find that users who are highly educated and working in professional occupations are more likely to use ChatGPT for work-related messages and for Asking rather than Doing messages at work.",
    "Overall, our findings suggest that ChatGPT has a broad-based impact on the global economy.",
    "The fact that non-work usage is increasing faster suggests that the welfare gains from generative AI usage could be substantial."
  ],
